subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national, regional and local level capacity to mainstream gender equality and women’s empowerment in government policies and institutions
subproject.description:
OUTPUT 1: Beneficiary women, local authorities and commercial actors will have greater capacity and knowledge that favor women’s participation in the labor force.
OUTPUT 2: Women's participation to employment and their earnings increased as a result of economic empowerment
